#. MovableFeatures.Text.Desc
msgctxt "MovableFeatures.Text.Desc"
msgid "Now more items in fixed positions can be moved!"
msgstr "Позволяет перемещать некоторые строения и гейзеры в желаемое место."

#. MovableFeatures.Text.GenerateUnobtanium
msgctxt "MovableFeatures.Text.GenerateUnobtanium"
msgid "Generate Unobtanium"
msgstr "Генерация нейтрония"

#. MovableFeatures.Text.GenerateUnobtaniumDesc
msgctxt "MovableFeatures.Text.GenerateUnobtaniumDesc"
msgid "Whether or not does moving a geyser create Unobtanium."
msgstr "Создаст ли гейзер нейтроний после перемещения."

#. MovableFeatures.Text.Name
msgctxt "MovableFeatures.Text.Name"
msgid "Movable Features"
msgstr "Перемещение объектов [Movable Features]"

#. MovableFeatures.Text.StableMode
msgctxt "MovableFeatures.Text.StableMode"
msgid "Stable Mode"
msgstr "Стабильный режим"

#. MovableFeatures.Text.StableModeDesc
msgctxt "MovableFeatures.Text.StableModeDesc"
msgid "If enabled, the save file needs to be reloaded after moving items."
msgstr "Если включено, то файл сохранения необходимо перезагрузить после перемещения предметов."

#. MovableFeatures.Text.ToggleGeyserNum
msgctxt "MovableFeatures.Text.ToggleGeyserNum"
msgid "Toggle Geyser Num"
msgstr "Номер гейзера"

#. MovableFeatures.Text.ToggleGeyserNumDesc
msgctxt "MovableFeatures.Text.ToggleGeyserNumDesc"
msgid "When moving a geyser, do not change its attributes."
msgstr "Перемещая гейзер, не изменять его атрибуты."
